ervations. In future studies, the new ISP corrected data can be used in\nconjunction with 3D radiative transfer models to better map the geometry of the\nejecta of SN 1993J.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Mar 2020 21:54:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-01"}
