e detected an increase by a factor of\nabout three in the flaring rate of the most luminous and most energetic flares\nthat have occurred since 2014 Aug. 30. The X-ray activity of Sgr A* has\nincreased for more than four years. Additional studies about the overall\nnear-infrared and radio behavior of Sgr A* are required to draw strong results\non the multiwavelength activity of the black hole.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Mar 2020 10:27:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-15"}
