 photosphere of W~Hya, which\nwe reproduce using models with an inner dust shell that is optically thick to\nscattering. The radial profile of the polarised light observed around W\\,Hya\nreveal a steep dust density profile. We find the wind-acceleration region of\nW\\,Hya to extend to at least $\\sim 7~R_\\star$, in agreement with theoretical\npredictions of acceleration up to $\\sim 12~R_\\star$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Mar 2020 10:51:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-16"}
