hat is\nthe case, photospheric emission during the early, prompt phase would be even\nmore dominant.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Mar 2020 12:23:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 19 Mar 2020 10:15:57 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 24 Mar 2020 10:43:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-06"}
